Final season tables -- Canterbury District Soccer Football Association 2023

First-grade teams are listed in bold.

For teams finishing on equal points, competition regulations specified that head-to-head results were used as the next tie-breaker, before overall goal difference.

In divisions which were split after a Stage One round-robin, the points gained in Stage One were carried forward to Stage Two.
